  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on <strong>Stormblades</strong>, the action adventure where tradition meets fierce combat. Take on the role of a young warrior in a sacred rite of passage through a world of ancient ruins and forgotten temples. Your mission: hunt down and defeat the legendary Keepers, creatures that protect ancient secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.poster.avif?t=1771615952\" width=508 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.webm?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.mp4?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Channel the mystical energy of the ruins by awakening ancient altars and strengthening your blade with the Essence of defeated enemies. Each victory brings you closer to becoming a legend—claim your opponents' Relics as proof of your conquest. Master the art of combat—dodge the Guardians' relentless attacks, counter with furious precision, and destroy their defenses with devastating blows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.poster.avif?t=1771615952\" width=508 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.webm?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.mp4?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stormblades Remastered </strong>returns with the fluid sword combat that made it famous, now more precise than ever.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic, action-packed sword combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your weapon and infuse it with mystical powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face ruthless enemies and colossal Guardians</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore jungles overgrown by nature and ruins forgotten by time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements to unlock as you master the way of the Warrior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with Warriors from around the world in pursuit of glory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save system to record your progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support for an enhanced experience</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on <strong>Stormblades</strong>, the action adventure where tradition meets fierce combat. Take on the role of a young warrior in a sacred rite of passage through a world of ancient ruins and forgotten temples. Your mission: hunt down and defeat the legendary Keepers, creatures that protect ancient secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.poster.avif?t=1771615952\" width=508 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.webm?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/9b1ef3bfb6b097adc74d59f627814956.mp4?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Channel the mystical energy of the ruins by awakening ancient altars and strengthening your blade with the Essence of defeated enemies. Each victory brings you closer to becoming a legend—claim your opponents' Relics as proof of your conquest. Master the art of combat—dodge the Guardians' relentless attacks, counter with furious precision, and destroy their defenses with devastating blows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.poster.avif?t=1771615952\" width=508 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.webm?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1358940/extras/198e3cefa8e8290961fa9c1beccaad70.mp4?t=1771615952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stormblades Remastered </strong>returns with the fluid sword combat that made it famous, now more precise than ever.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic, action-packed sword combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your weapon and infuse it with mystical powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face ruthless enemies and colossal Guardians</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore jungles overgrown by nature and ruins forgotten by time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements to unlock as you master the way of the Warrior</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with Warriors from around the world in pursuit of glory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save system to record your progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full controller support for an enhanced experience</p></li></ul>",
